description: anytime code needs to be run, run via `uv`
alwaysApply: false
---
please use `uv` to run all code and tests with the proper environment. examples:
- `uv run script.py`
- `uv run pytest tests/`
- `uv run python -c "import <package>"`

new packages can be added to the environment by running `uv add <package>`.